  "Description": {
    "English": "A technology module harvested from the remains of a salvaged starship. May also be collected from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">freighter crash sites</span> or salvaged during <span class=\"name name-stellar\">frigate expeditions</span>.<br><br>At the appropriate <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Outfitters</span>, may be used to expand starship storage capacity.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船残骸</span>里采集出来的技术模块。也可以从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船失事地点</span>获得，或在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰远征</span>期间回收。<br><br>你可以前往空间站的<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船装备装置</span>使用它来扩充飞船的仓储容量。",
    "TencentChinese": "取自大型飞船残骸的一种技术模块。可以从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船坠毁地点</span>收集，或在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">护卫舰远征</span>期间回收。<br><br>当前状态下毫无用处，你货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">研究站</span>也许能把它转化成可用的技术。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從一艘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">回收的太空船</span>收集的科技模組。可以從<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船墜機地點</span>收集，或在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡防艦探勘</span>中回收。<br><br>可在太空站的<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船改造站</span>中，將其用於擴充太空船倉儲空間。"
  },
